Class BreakerAnalogGyro

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.BreakerLib.devices.sensors.gyro.BreakerAnalogGyro
All Implemented Interfaces:
BreakerGenericGyro
public class BreakerAnalogGyro
extends java.lang.Object
implements BreakerGenericGyro
Single-axis gyro connected to analog ports of RoboRIO. Gyro is initialized on construction.
